{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"620af6dec5","title":"致彭德怀电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"94e00158bb","index":0,"year":1935,"month":10,"day":14,"articleId":"620af6dec5"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"312478c42a","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀电\"","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"620af6dec5"},{"id":"569b98b0ae","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年10月14日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"620af6dec5"},{"id":"9dd75fa0ea","type":"paragraph","text":"二、三纵队必须乘夜通过洪德城、环县之线，明日到耿家湾（不含）以南地区宿营，后日与一纵队取平行路东进。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"620af6dec5"},{"id":"aa243e7c25","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东在洪德城致彭德怀电的主要内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"620af6dec5"},{"id":"e589e7cb5a","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]关于陕甘支队通过洪德城的情况，毛泽东在10月22日中共中央政治局会议上说：洪德城是最危险的一关。我们过渭水后，敌人知道了底细，即急风暴雨般地追击。我们通过洪德城后，敌人二点半即到，如不早通过，要受阻碍。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"620af6dec5"}],"page":{"id":"54e09c7c65","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"620af6dec5","start":241,"end":241}}}},"__N_SSG":true}